Really?  I've seen perhaps 5 rooms in hard LDON (I haven't done a guk, but I've done lots of the other four) over all the maps where I get more than, say, 3 at a time.  If/when that happens, I usually fade off and snag a couple singles.  My normal hard group can handle 4 though (my shaman always malos' everything very fast, as per my request) as long as they come in STAGGERED &lt;--that's the key.  Most pulls are 2.  I could probably pull 80% of every hard ldon with ANY class and be okay, because it's all about recognizing what mobs will come and what mobs will not come.  The other 20% of the time, I actually need to split, and when that time comes, I /hug fading memories and split <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START ;) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/wink.gif ALT=";)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <br>
