<br>
While a good bard can often force through a normal LDoN win with a marginal group, that same bard is unlikely to do so in a high risk LDoN.  [I can recall being stymied once by a tank who for some reason involving THC couldn't get aggro from a snared mob walking slowly past him towards me.]<br>
