<br>
There is one big thing that seperates the good hard LDON pullers from the bad ones, the good ones are going to con every mob before touching them, and con every mob that might assist that mob.<br>
<br>
Lower level mobs assist shorter ranged calls for aggro, so sometimes lower lvl mobs that would add if they were white wont add because they are blue, just like you can single pull all day any camp 11+ lvls lower till u are blue in the face since aggro range modifiers make assist aggro pretty much disappear in those cases most of the time.<br>
<br>
If you have to decide which of the 2 to cast on, cast on the blue one, I prefer mez on the blue one straight off and then remez if it didnt take instead of wasting time HOSing, mez has a fairly good land rate on the blues in 65 hard.<br>
