don't be afriad to kite the pulls around the room before, or even in your groups room till u can land a mez<br>
a well placed lull to break the chain, pull with mez, get 2 on the pull, mez one.....bring other to group, then head back to mez the first as its INC to your group, recylce to your first mezzed, hit it again and usually your group will have the first one near dead......mez fades and boom, you got another mob right as your group finishes off the first<br>
was a thrill to say the least, i think i like ldon<br>
